{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/JavaScript/closure/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"leo-xee.io","author":"Leo-Xee","siteUrl":"https://leo-xee.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"leo-xee/blog-comments"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"leoxexe"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8c10b167-02d2-53c9-b01c-7839e7f29cb8","excerpt":"클로저란? 클로저(Closure)란, 내부함수가 외부함수의 지역변수를 참조할 때 외부함수가 소멸(종료)된 후에도 내부함수가 외부함수의 지역변수를 참조할 수 있는 현상을 일컫는다. 위의 설명을 보고 전혀 감이 오지 않을 것이다. 그게 정상이다. 클로저는 단번에 이해하기 쉬운 개념이 아닌 것 같다.\n아래의 한 가지 예제를 통해 클로저를 이해해보도록 하자. 아래의 GIF는 클로저가 발생한 소스코드의 전체 실행 과정인데 이를 한 단계씩 알아볼 것이다. 그림…","html":"<p><img src=\"/b6422d8815031d57cf3948e4032caf37/thumbNail.gif\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"클로저란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%81%B4%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%80%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"클로저란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>클로저란?</h1>\n<p><strong>클로저(Closure)란, 내부함수가 외부함수의 지역변수를 참조할 때 외부함수가 소멸(종료)된 후에도 내부함수가 외부함수의 지역변수를 참조할 수 있는 현상을 일컫는다.</strong></p>\n<p>위의 설명을 보고 전혀 감이 오지 않을 것이다. 그게 정상이다. 클로저는 단번에 이해하기 쉬운 개념이 아닌 것 같다.\n아래의 한 가지 예제를 통해 클로저를 이해해보도록 하자.</p>\n<p>아래의 GIF는 클로저가 발생한 소스코드의 전체 실행 과정인데 이를 한 단계씩 알아볼 것이다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/a19ca8ddaa5b34864d59538502c439af/closure-01.gif\" alt=\"그림1. 클로저의 발생 과정\"></p>\n<br/>\n<ol>\n<li>먼저 전역 실행 컨텍스트가 열리고 <code class=\"language-text\">environmentRecord</code>에 전역 공간의 식별 정보를 수집한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림2. 클로저 1번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림2. 클로저 1번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/205028de898ac2901695370d5699f07e/c1b63/closure-02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/205028de898ac2901695370d5699f07e/5a46d/closure-02.png 300w,\n/static/205028de898ac2901695370d5699f07e/0a47e/closure-02.png 600w,\n/static/205028de898ac2901695370d5699f07e/c1b63/closure-02.png 1200w,\n/static/205028de898ac2901695370d5699f07e/b1001/closure-02.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">outer()</code>를 실행하기 위해서 <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code> 실행 컨텍스트가 열리고 식별 정보를 <code class=\"language-text\">environmentRecord</code>에 수집한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림3. 클로저 2번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림3. 클로저 2번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/0fa94cc1e0a22a4ee0ad873e01e6b650/c1b63/closure-03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0fa94cc1e0a22a4ee0ad873e01e6b650/5a46d/closure-03.png 300w,\n/static/0fa94cc1e0a22a4ee0ad873e01e6b650/0a47e/closure-03.png 600w,\n/static/0fa94cc1e0a22a4ee0ad873e01e6b650/c1b63/closure-03.png 1200w,\n/static/0fa94cc1e0a22a4ee0ad873e01e6b650/b1001/closure-03.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">outer()</code>의 반환 값으로 <code class=\"language-text\">inner</code>함수를 반환하고 <code class=\"language-text\">outer2</code>에 할당한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림4. 클로저 3번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림4. 클로저 3번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/59b1f541dc83c5daae4ca81c6688997f/c1b63/closure-04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/59b1f541dc83c5daae4ca81c6688997f/5a46d/closure-04.png 300w,\n/static/59b1f541dc83c5daae4ca81c6688997f/0a47e/closure-04.png 600w,\n/static/59b1f541dc83c5daae4ca81c6688997f/c1b63/closure-04.png 1200w,\n/static/59b1f541dc83c5daae4ca81c6688997f/b1001/closure-04.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>원래는 <code class=\"language-text\">outer</code>함수의 실행이 종료됨과 동시에 <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code> 실행 컨텍스트도 소멸되어야한다. 하지만 <code class=\"language-text\">outer</code>함수의 지역변수 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">outer2</code>에 할당된 <code class=\"language-text\">inner</code>함수를 통해서 참조될 수 있기 때문에(<strong><code class=\"language-text\">a</code>의 참조 카운트가 남아있다고 표현한다.</strong>) <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code> 실행 컨텍스트의 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>는 소멸되지 않고 남아있다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림5. 클로저 4번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림5. 클로저 4번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/327458ed96bc525c83c040554a38dfc5/c1b63/closure-05.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/327458ed96bc525c83c040554a38dfc5/5a46d/closure-05.png 300w,\n/static/327458ed96bc525c83c040554a38dfc5/0a47e/closure-05.png 600w,\n/static/327458ed96bc525c83c040554a38dfc5/c1b63/closure-05.png 1200w,\n/static/327458ed96bc525c83c040554a38dfc5/b1001/closure-05.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>이제 <code class=\"language-text\">outer2</code>를 실행한다. 이는 할당된 <code class=\"language-text\">inner</code>함수를 실행하는 것과 동일하기 때문에 <code class=\"language-text\">Inner</code> 실행 컨텍스트가 열리고 <code class=\"language-text\">outerEnvironmentReference</code>를 통해서 <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code> 실행 컨텍스트의 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>를 찾아서 <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>만큼 증가시킨 <code class=\"language-text\">2</code>를 반환하고 <code class=\"language-text\">Inner</code> 실행 컨텍스트는 소멸된다. 하지만 <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code> 실행 컨텍스트의 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>는 여전히 남아있다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림6. 클로저 5번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림6. 클로저 5번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/89999d446c49c3ecaab80e766199d2a9/c1b63/closure-06.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/89999d446c49c3ecaab80e766199d2a9/5a46d/closure-06.png 300w,\n/static/89999d446c49c3ecaab80e766199d2a9/0a47e/closure-06.png 600w,\n/static/89999d446c49c3ecaab80e766199d2a9/c1b63/closure-06.png 1200w,\n/static/89999d446c49c3ecaab80e766199d2a9/b1001/closure-06.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>반환 받은 값인 <code class=\"language-text\">2</code>를 콘솔에 출력한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림7. 클로저 6번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림7. 클로저 6번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/73ea38f9c41deac9086873a1e6be21f9/c1b63/closure-07.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/73ea38f9c41deac9086873a1e6be21f9/5a46d/closure-07.png 300w,\n/static/73ea38f9c41deac9086873a1e6be21f9/0a47e/closure-07.png 600w,\n/static/73ea38f9c41deac9086873a1e6be21f9/c1b63/closure-07.png 1200w,\n/static/73ea38f9c41deac9086873a1e6be21f9/b1001/closure-07.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>5번과 동일하게 동작하지만 <code class=\"language-text\">2</code>를 <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>만큼 증가시킨 <code class=\"language-text\">3</code>을 반환한다. 마찬가지로 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>의 참조카운트가 유효하기 때문에 <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code> 실행 컨텍스트의 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>는 남아 있다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림8. 클로저 7번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림8. 클로저 7번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/78eec776a50b46f29e4e71a92279370b/c1b63/closure-08.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/78eec776a50b46f29e4e71a92279370b/5a46d/closure-08.png 300w,\n/static/78eec776a50b46f29e4e71a92279370b/0a47e/closure-08.png 600w,\n/static/78eec776a50b46f29e4e71a92279370b/c1b63/closure-08.png 1200w,\n/static/78eec776a50b46f29e4e71a92279370b/b1001/closure-08.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>반환 값인 <code class=\"language-text\">3</code>을 콘솔에 출력한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림9. 클로저 8번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림9. 클로저 8번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/eed6648bb975b93d0428af47768259f8/c1b63/closure-09.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eed6648bb975b93d0428af47768259f8/5a46d/closure-09.png 300w,\n/static/eed6648bb975b93d0428af47768259f8/0a47e/closure-09.png 600w,\n/static/eed6648bb975b93d0428af47768259f8/c1b63/closure-09.png 1200w,\n/static/eed6648bb975b93d0428af47768259f8/b1001/closure-09.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li>실행이 종료된다. 하지만 <code class=\"language-text\">outer2</code>에 할당된 <code class=\"language-text\">inner</code>함수가 여전히 <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code> 실행 컨텍스트의 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>를 참조하고 있다. 그렇기 때문에 <code class=\"language-text\">outer2</code>에 다른 값을 재할당해서 참조를 끊지 않는 이상 Outer 실행 컨텍스트의 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>값은 계속 남아 있다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"그림10. 클로저 9번 과정\"\n        title=\"그림10. 클로저 9번 과정\"\n        src=\"/static/789e94c689974925fd150b34b389efad/c1b63/closure-10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/789e94c689974925fd150b34b389efad/5a46d/closure-10.png 300w,\n/static/789e94c689974925fd150b34b389efad/0a47e/closure-10.png 600w,\n/static/789e94c689974925fd150b34b389efad/c1b63/closure-10.png 1200w,\n/static/789e94c689974925fd150b34b389efad/b1001/closure-10.png 1380w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"클로저를-사용하는-이유\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%81%B4%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%80%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0\" aria-label=\"클로저를 사용하는 이유 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>클로저를 사용하는 이유?</h1>\n<p>이러한 클로저를 사용하면 이점은 크게 3가지가 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>접근 권한 제어</li>\n<li>지역변수 보호</li>\n<li>데이터 보존 및 활용</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">user</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">_name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> _logged <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span> <span class=\"token function\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> _name\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">set</span> <span class=\"token function\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">v</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      _name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> v\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">login</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      _logged <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">logout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      _logged <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">get</span> <span class=\"token function\">status</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> _logged <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string\">'login'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'logout'</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation